Datatec Expects Its Revenue to Increase to as Much as $5.1 Billion in 2012

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-11T06:08:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/datatec-expects-its-revenue-to-increase-to-as-much-as-5-1-billion-in-2012.html
Datatec Ltd. (DTC)  said it expects to
report revenue of between $4.8 billion and $5.1 billion for the
2012 financial year, with a further expansion of operating
margins.  Profit after tax is seen at about $84 million, the company
said in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  